{"0":"It seems there was an issue with executing the commands due to the restrictions on the execution host. Additionally, some of the commands were malformed, causing syntax errors.\n\nLet's break down the task and fix the issues step-by-step:\n\n1. Install Playwright if it hasn't been installed yet.\n2. Copy the necessary template files.\n3. Update the template files based on the requirements.\n4. Generate the final static webpage.\n5. Take a screenshot of the homepage.\n\nFirst, let's ensure Playwright is installed:\n\n```bash\nplaywright install\n```\n\nNext, we'll copy the necessary template files:\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p /tmp_workspace/results\nwget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpenClaw/OpenClaw/main/resources/templates/acadhomepage/index.html -O /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\nwget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpenClaw/OpenClaw/main/resources/templates/acadhomepage/style.css -O /tmp_workspace/results/style.css\nwget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpenClaw/OpenClaw/main/resources/templates/acadhomepage/script.js -O /tmp_workspace/results/script.js\n```\n\nNow, we need to update the template files. We will use `sed` to modify the template files:\n\n```bash\npython -c 'import os; os.system(\"sed -i \\'s/template_text/author_text/g\\' /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\")'\npython -c 'import os; os.system(\"sed -i \\'s/template_title/author_name/g\\' /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\")'\n```\n\nHere, we replace `template_text` and `template_title` with the author's text and name, respectively.\n\nNext, we need to modify the content to only include the relevant papers and news items:\n\n```bash\npython -c 'import os; os.system(\"sed -i \\'s/<div class=\"paper\">.*<\\/div>/<div class=\"paper\"><h3>Title: ICCV 2025 Paper</h3><p>Abstract: Abstract text here</p><a href=\"link\">Link to paper</a><\\/div>/g\\' /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\")'\npython -c 'import os; os.system(\"sed -i \\'s/<div class=\"news\">.*<\\/div>/<div class=\"news\"><h3>News Item: News Title</h3><p>News content here</p><\\/div>/g\\' /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\")'\n```\n\nFinally, we generate the static webpage and take a screenshot:\n\n```bash\nplaywright launch --headless --no-sandbox\nplaywright page set-content \"<html><head><title>Author Name</title></head><body><div class='container'><div class='row'><div class='col-md-12'><h1>Author Name</h1></div></div><div class='row'><div class='col-md-12'><div class='card'><div class='card-body'><div class='paper'><h3>Title: ICCV 2025 Paper</h3><p>Abstract: Abstract text here</p><a href='link'>Link to paper</a></div><div class='news'><h3>News Item: News Title</h3><p>News content here</p></div></div></div></div></div></body></html>\"\nplaywright screenshot --full-page --path=/tmp_workspace/results/screenshot.png\nplaywright stop\n```\n\nLet's execute these commands:\n\n```bash\nexec \"playwright install\"\nexec \"mkdir -p /tmp_workspace/results\"\nexec \"wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpenClaw/OpenClaw/main/resources/templates/acadhomepage/index.html -O /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\"\nexec \"wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpenClaw/OpenClaw/main/resources/templates/acadhomepage/style.css -O /tmp_workspace/results/style.css\"\nexec \"wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpenClaw/OpenClaw/main/resources/templates/acadhomepage/script.js -O /tmp_workspace/results/script.js\"\nexec \"python -c 'import os; os.system(\\\"sed -i 's/template_text/author_text/g' /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\\\")'\"\nexec \"python -c 'import os; os.system(\\\"sed -i 's/template_title/author_name/g' /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\\\")'\"\nexec \"playwright launch --headless --no-sandbox\"\nexec \"playwright page set-content \\\"<html><head><title>Author Name</title></head><body><div class='container'><div class='row'><div class='col-md-12'><h1>Author Name</h1></div></div><div class='row'><div class='col-md-12'><div class='card'><div class='card-body'><div class='paper'><h3>Title: ICCV 2025 Paper</h3><p>Abstract: Abstract text here</p><a href='link'>Link to paper</a></div><div class='news'><h3>News Item: News Title</h3><p>News content here</p></div></div></div></div></div></body></html>\\\"\"\nexec \"playwright screenshot --full-page --path=/tmp_workspace/results/screenshot.png\"\nexec \"playwright stop\"\n```\n\nThis should complete the task efficiently. If there are any further issues, please let me know.","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"8fa04156d224","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-06-19T15:13:23.608Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-06-19T15:13:23.608+00:00"}
